{
  "name": "Striking Stance Viper",
  "type": "spell",
  "img": "systems/n5eb/assets/Icons%20%26%20Images/Clans/Hebi.png",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You can only gain the benefit from one Striking Stance at a time. <br />If you enter another Striking Stance while currently benefiting from this one, the one immediately ends. <br />You do not spend Chakra to maintain this Jutsu. <br />You enter the poisonous stance of a Viper. <br />For the duration, weapon attacks and Hebi clan Bukijutsu cast using one of this jutsu's components ignore slashing resistance and pierces damage reduction, instead dealing direct damage to the target creature. <br />Additionally, the component weapons chosen can now be used as components with Bukijutsu that requires Melee Piercing.</p>",
